Give Agents Access to Work Summaries

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on.

Manage Profiles and Permission Sets

Select agents or profiles to use Work Summaries.
Assign selected agents the Work Summaries User permission set (included with the Einstein for Service add-on license).

If Work Summaries is enabled, users with this permission get access to the Wrap Up component in the service console.

(Optional) To use Work Summaries in copilot, assign agents the Use Einstein Copilot for Salesforce user permission and the Prompt Template user permission.
title: Give Agents Access to Work Summaries
